name: Openstreetmap Geofabrik, Poland Points of Interest, Poland, 2008
description: This dataset shows points of interest in Poland. Features included in this dataset include, libraries, post offices, places of worship, parking, restaurants, cafes, fuel, parking, police, theaters, cinemas, prisons, universities, camp sites and other public places. there are over 1,500 points of interest included.
